{
  "stem": "13690.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I could see there was no room-- that each room was having pritchers of two, three level pritchers--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bunks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no room for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said there is no way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, go back where?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I said I'm going to go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the town of Radomsko was 70 kilometers away from-- from my home town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I got an idea but-- that the Jews who were rounded up in that truck that I was there with, they were told that their personal possessions-- they were so accurate, they said don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Leave your possessions.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next truck will come with the possessions after it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they brought it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it came to my mind when this--the truck came back, brought all those belongings to the Jews, I jumped and I went and I jumped on top of that truck.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And where was that truck heading to?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That truck was heading back to the town that I was born, to Zarki.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was quite an interesting trip to go back in that truck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, I jumped at the truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He did not know that I am in the truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then finally, then-- it was-- that was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I have to take a break.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The truck was powered by woods, so they had a certain area there where I could go into the to that compartment, and I went into the compartment.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I covered myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I covered myself with this, just not to freeze.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So while I was going on-- the truck was going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not even realized where he's heading or where he's going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Seemingly half-way he stopped the truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
